        This candidate will be responsible for: &nbsp &nbsp
        ●Apply machine learning and predictive modeling techniques across the business.
        ●Developing commercially available solutions using OSS, Windows, Azure, Bing, and Office technologies.
        ●Technical subject matter expertise in OSS and Microsoft technologies to build code and other technical content to support developer events, architecture design sessions, and resolve issues. &nbsp
        ●Providing subject matter expertise and leadership to Microsoft teams worldwide.
        ●Working closely with Microsoft teams to influence the future product roadmap.
        ●Developing and driving new ways of thinking across groups within the division to improve quality, engineering productivity, and responsiveness to feedback and changing priorities.
